what_worked: Applied decorrelate, date_cte_isolate, multi_dimension_prefetch: Pushed selective dimension filters (date_dim.year=2002, item.category/manager) into separate CTEs before joining with inventory, converted implicit joins to explicit JOIN syntax, and pre-filtered months (10,11) early in date_dim CTE.
why_it_worked: Correlated subqueries re-execute per outer row; converting to JOIN eliminates per-row overhead; Pre-filtering date dimension into CTE reduces hash join probe table from 73K to ~365 rows; Pre-filtering multiple dimension tables in parallel reduces join fan-out
